Probability of Detection
POD can be determined using either the “POD vs. Coverage” graph or 
using a standard scientific calculator:
1. Enter Coverage (C) into the calculator, gives “C”;
2. Push the “change sign” key once (+/-), gives “-C”;
3. Push the “ex
” key (many calculators push the “2nd” or “Inv” key 
followed by the “LN” key, which has small “ex
” above), gives e-C;
4. Push the “-“ key or subtraction key, gives –e
-C
;
5. Push the “1” key (1), gives 1 – e
-C
;
6. Push the “equals” key (=), gives –POD;
7. Push the “change sign” key (+/-), result is POD.
