C1 2.8 mi 0.7 mi 60 ft
C2 2.0 mi 0.5 mi 60 ft
Did you notice the searchers in Region A are only searching for half of the 
time until sunset, and that segment C1 requires searching close to sunset 
not counting travel time to the site? What can you do to change this?
Try again, this time using multiple tracks. What happens to your effort 
when you switch some of your segment baselines and lengths?
