Searchers = (A7x5280)/(A11bxA10xB14)
Spacing = W/C = A9/B15
This page shows an example of 
working backwards from a 
“desired POD” to determine the 
number of searchers required.
Note rounding adjusted to 
ensure segment POCs add up 
to full region POC (100%).

